quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  30,25,"Ndipo pakati pa zizindikiro zake ndi chakuti kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi zimadzichepetsa potsatira malamulo ake ndipo pamene Iye akuitanani inu kamodzi kokha kuchokera mâ€™nthaka, Taonani inu mudzadza mwamsanga msanga"
  30,26,Ndipo chilichonse chimene chili kumwamba ndi padziko lapansi ndi chake ndipo zonse zimamumvera Iye
  30,27,Ndipo Iye ndiye amene amayambitsa chilengedwe ndipo adzachibwerezanso ndipo zimenezi ndi zapafupi kwa Iye. Ndipo wake ndi ulemerero kumwamba ndi padziko lapansi. Ndipo Iye ndiye Mwini mphamvu zonse ndi Mwini nzeru zonse
  30,28,Iye ali kupereka chitsanzo chokhudza inu nomwe. Kodi inu muli nawo akapolo amene amakhala anzanu pa zinthu zimene takupatsani ndipo kuti mumagawana nawo zinthuzo mofanana ndiponso mumawaopa iwo monga momwe mumaoperana? Mmenemo ndi mmene timasiyanitsira chiphunzitso chathu kwa anthu amene amazindikira
  30,29,Iyayi! onse osalungama amatsatira zilakolako zawo mosadziwa. Kotero ndani angatsogolere iye amene Mulungu wamusocheretsa? Ndipo iwo sadzakhala ndi wowathandiza
  30,30,"Kotero dzipereke kwathunthu ku chipembedzo choonadi, chipembedzo, chenicheni, chimene Mulungu adalamula kuti munthu ayenera kutsatira. Chilengedwe chimene Mulungu adalenga mtundu wa anthu sichingasinthidwe. Ndithudi pali Mulungu, icho ndicho chipembedzo choona. Koma ambiri a mtundu wa anthu sadziwa"
  30,31,Lapani kwa Iye ndiponso muopeni Iye. Pitirizani kupemphera nthawi zonse ndipo musakhale inu pakati pa iwo amene amafanizira milungu ina ndi Mulungu weniweni
  30,32,Pali anthu amene amagawa chipembedzo chawo ndi kukhala mipingo yosiyanasiyana ndipo mpingo uliwonse umasangalala ndi zimene uli nazo